  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/11452883c3fd29a80c99fd8684403c2a.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>With tons of action and adrenaline, we bring you only the most exciting part of arcade soccer!<br>Play in single-player mode or local multiplayer. You can even share the game using Remote Play Together!<br>Up to 4 players can enjoy playing competitively or cooperatively across any game mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/f622d8ea8ea563655fbb96a4bf4642ed.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play modes:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/dab3e3e103a5a5c074cb7bb5d01fd8cb.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ol><li> Friendly match and penalty shootouts<br></li><li> Tournaments - play the most important competitions!<br></li><li> Career Mode! - create your team from scratch and lead it to glory!<br></li><li> Themed Events - crazy game modes with amazing characters.<br></li><li> Party tournaments - have fun with friends and family!</li></ol><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Store:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/7d0794f67dc0774b80d8cdd827035d04.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/7d0794f67dc0774b80d8cdd827035d04.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/7d0794f67dc0774b80d8cdd827035d04.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you play, you'll earn coins, which you can use in the store to purchase original items, such as balls, flags, stadiums, and also cosmetics for your players and teams... from unique hairstyles to a lion costume, anything is possible!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Available tournaments:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/3199bdee4d3964a0d8ea58db6d7931db.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Charrua Tournament and Charrua A and B Leagues<br></li><li> European, American and Asian Cups<br></li><li> Olymcharrua Cups (male and female)<br></li><li> Global Cup (male and female)<br></li><li> Global Cup 1930 (evoking the first international cup with a retro touch)<br></li><li> USA Leagues (male and female), Eurochamp League and Liberty Cup</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characteristics:</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/16b3ae88c575f45ffa069fb6b5aeea76.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Easy to learn and enjoy, with clean and challenging gameplay.<br></li><li> Two controls modes, to suit occasional players and also more experienced ones.<br></li><li> Configurable assisted mode, to help you in the actions you prefer or disable it to increase the challenge.<br></li><li> Fouls, free kicks, yellow and red cards, injuries, and penalties!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/91b6911346ec757457173951f060a2cf.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Women's, men's, and mixed soccer.<br></li><li> Short, long or through passes... directed, controlled or elevated shots... and also Chilean kicks, scorpion, scissors, pigeon header, etc.<br></li><li> Manage team formation and strategy, player changes and much more.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.poster.avif?t=1702301039\" width=602 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.webm?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283380/extras/38369c22777e56eda58069a8e9f709f0.mp4?t=1702301039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Whether you are a soccer fan or not so much, this game will keep you entertained for hours!<br>Do you have what it takes to become a champion?</strong>",
